org.obd.query
Class ComparisonQueryTerm

java.lang.Object
  org.obd.query.QueryTerm
      org.obd.query.ComparisonQueryTerm

public class ComparisonQueryTerm
extends QueryTerm

A QueryTerm comparing two values

Example: LabelQueryTerm(ComparisonQueryTerm(STARTS_WITH, "transcription")) => matches entities whose label starts with "transcription"

cjm
